		<div id="main-info" class="content">
			<p id="roles">Solo project – all assets are my own</p>
			<p>An endless runner game with a character you can’t control, players must guide their robot by drawing platforms on screen to avoid obstacles and collect energy to get as far as they can.</p>
			<img src="Media/Main/SplineDraw.png">
			<p>Optimized for mobile, spline-rider is a very lightweight, simple and easy to pick up. It features a one button control scheme – the only way to play is to draw on the screen, but procedurally generated obstacles make for interesting challenges and plenty of emergent gameplay.</p>
			<p>The game features collectable coins and an in-game shop to spend them, with a simple save system to store currency and equipped/unlocked customizations.</p>
			<img src="Media/Main/SplineDraw.png">
			<p>Spline rider will be available on PC and Android devices later this year</p>
